                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dear customer, I really must tell you about the time when our humble store received a famous stone that would shake Liyue to its core. Now, where should I start concerning that stone? Ah, yes. It all started when a hero discovered several suspicious hilichurls...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: When Action Phase begins, the active characters on both sides will be affected by Hydro",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Hint: A battle in the rain will cause both sides to trigger Elemental Reactions more easily!",
